import React from 'react'
import * as S from './styles'
import {constants} from './constants'

const NavigationMenu = () => {
  return (
    <S.NavigationMenu>
      <S.MenuItem to="/">
        <S.IconWrapper>
          {constants}
        </S.IconWrapper>
        <S.Title>Home</S.Title>
      </S.MenuItem>
      <S.MenuItem to="/about">
        <S.IconWrapper>
          <BiTask />

        <S.Title>Home</S.Title>
      </S.MenuItem>
      <S.MenuItem to="/ehmed">
        <S.IconWrapper>
          <AiOutlineHome />
        </S.IconWrapper>
        <S.Title>Home</S.Title>
      </S.MenuItem>
      <S.MenuItem to="/memmed">
        <S.IconWrapper>
          <AiOutlineHome />
        </S.IconWrapper>
        <S.Title>Home</S.Title>
      </S.MenuItem>
    </S.NavigationMenu>
  );
}

export {NavigationMenu}
